Package: ActioneeR
Version: 0.1
Date: 2022-06-01
Title: Package to manage imagery and data from cameras in the field.
Description: This package contains function to help copy, rename, download and organise files from camera to the HDD. The package want to make these processes more efficient when in the field it is needed to copy a large number of files. Organizing files in the correct fodler hierarchy will help the processing of these at a later stage. 
Author: Filippo Ferrario <filippo.f3rrario@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Filippo Ferrario <filippo.f3rrario@gmail.com>
Depends: exiftoolr
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
